The paper deals with machine learning algorithms for prediction, specifically Prediction with Expert Advice. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the analysis of loss bounds, which is related to information theory (cs.IT) and game theory (cs.GT). Finally, the use of adaptive learning rates and the tuning of parameters is a common theme in data science (cs.DS).
